<h1>PRIVACY POLICY</h1>

<p>
Homemaker’s Media Group Ltd. (<strong>Ultimate Bundles</strong>) considers the privacy and security of user information an important component of the services offered at its website, www.mynewnormal.com (the Site). The following information explains how Ultimate Bundles collects and uses information obtained from users in connection with services available at the Site (taken together, the <strong>Service</strong>).
</p>
<p>
    <strong>Information Collected.</strong>
</p>
<p>
At your election, you may request additional information about Ultimate Bundles. When you do so, you may need to submit certain information or data to Ultimate Bundles, for example, your contact information (collectively, <strong>User Data</strong>).
</p>
<p>
