</p>
<p>
    <strong>Use of Information.</strong>
</p>
<p>
Ultimate Bundles uses User Data to respond to your inquiries for additional information.
</p>
<p>
Ultimate Bundles uses "traffic data" to help diagnose problems with its server, analyze trends and administer the Site. Your IP address is not linked to personally identifiable information, but is used to gather broad demographic data and to monitor statistics to improve the Site and Service.
</p>
<p>
    <strong>Sharing of Information.</strong>
</p>
<p>
